{
  "stem": "19895.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 135.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Day after day after day, just what went on, starvation, death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were sleeping next to each other in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he was more and more passive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And one day, this Jewish doctor, who came to make rounds of-- for people, like in a hospital, making rounds, to see why somebody couldn't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because we were, again, organized into units.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the unit commander was a jupo, Jude Polizei, a Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In other camps, as I found out later, they called them different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were called kapos, camp polizei.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "In this location, the name was Jude Polizei, jupo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "These jupos sometimes were rather rough on the Jewish fellows.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they were making us move and get out and work, because they had to produce numbers, how many people goes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And freezing cold outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Snow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Ice.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I had a pick which I had to move the earth, the dirt, with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I-- each of my raising that pick and-- and-- and shovel did not generate too much to achieve.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the Arrow Cross people and the German guards around us were terrorizing us that I'll kill you if you don't move on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And-- and the conversation was often German words shouted at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And stinking Jew, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And move on and work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I kill you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they were shooting people and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was-- it was terror, terror, terror.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Starvation, typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was inhumane.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Time went on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And one morning this Jewish doctors who came in-- I couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I was very exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And this Tomas Stern, my friend, said that he is unable to get up and move.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so these Jewish doctors asked us, well, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they checked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
